@startuml Seq11_AiFinanceChatbot
!theme plain
participant User
participant "React Frontend\n(Chat UI)" as Frontend
participant "Chat API" as Backend
participant "Intent\nRecognition" as IntentEng
participant "Data\nFetcher" as DataFetcher
participant "LLM API\n(Gemini/Groq)" as LLM
participant "MySQL DB" as DB

autonumber

Note over User,DB: **USER SENDS MESSAGE**

User -> Frontend: Type message in chat
User -> Frontend: "How much did I spend on food this month?"
User -> Frontend: Click "Send"

Frontend -> Frontend: Validate message length
Frontend -> Frontend: Show message in chat UI (User side)

Frontend -> Frontend: Show "Assistant typing..." indicator

Frontend -> Backend: POST /chat/message\n{user_id, message, chat_history}

Backend -> Backend: Store message in memory/session

Note over User,DB: **INTENT RECOGNITION**

Backend -> IntentEng: recognize_intent(message)

IntentEng -> IntentEng: Parse message for intent
IntentEng -> IntentEng: Extract keywords

Note over IntentEng: Intent Classification:
Note over IntentEng: - BUDGET_QUERY: "budget", "spent", "expense"
Note over IntentEng: - SPENDING_ANALYSIS: "analyze", "trend", "pattern"
Note over IntentEng: - GOAL_STATUS: "goal", "progress", "savings"
Note over IntentEng: - RECOMMENDATION: "suggest", "recommend", "how to save"
Note over IntentEng: - GENERAL_FINANCE: "help", "explain", "about"

IntentEng -> IntentEng: Message intent = "BUDGET_QUERY"
IntentEng -> IntentEng: Extract parameters: category="food", period="month"

IntentEng --> Backend: {intent: "BUDGET_QUERY",\nconfidence: 0.95,\nparameters: {category: "food", period: "month"}}

Note over User,DB: **FETCH RELEVANT DATA**

Backend -> DataFetcher: fetch_context(intent, parameters)

alt Intent: BUDGET_QUERY
    DataFetcher -> DB: SELECT SUM(amount) FROM transactions\n WHERE category='Food' AND date IN current_month
    DB --> DataFetcher: total_spent = 2100
    
    DataFetcher -> DB: SELECT SUM(amount) FROM budgets\nWHERE category='Food'
    DB --> DataFetcher: budget_limit = 2000
    
    DataFetcher -> DataFetcher: Calculate variance
    DataFetcher -> DataFetcher: overspent_by = 100 (5%)
    
    DataFetcher --> Backend: {category: "Food",\nspent: 2100, budget: 2000,\nvariance: +100, variance_percent: 5}

else Intent: SPENDING_ANALYSIS
    DataFetcher -> DB: Fetch last 3 months spending
    DB --> DataFetcher: monthly_data
    
    DataFetcher -> Analytics: Calculate trends
    DataFetcher --> Backend: {trend: "increasing",\npercentage_change: "+8.3%"}

else Intent: GOAL_STATUS
    DataFetcher -> DB: SELECT * FROM savings_goals
    DB --> DataFetcher: goals_data
    
    DataFetcher --> Backend: {goals: [...]}

else Intent: RECOMMENDATION
    DataFetcher -> DB: Fetch spending patterns
    DataFetcher --> Backend: {patterns: {...}}

end

Backend --> Frontend: {status: "processing"}

Note over User,DB: **GENERATE LLM RESPONSE**

Backend -> LLM: POST /generate-chat-response

Backend -> LLM: Prepare context prompt

Note over Backend: Context Prompt:
Note over Backend: "User data context:"
Note over Backend: "- Total food spending this month: ₹2,100"
Note over Backend: "- Food budget: ₹2,000"
Note over Backend: "- Overspent: ₹100 (5%)"
Note over Backend: "- Last month food: ₹1,950"
Note over Backend: "- Trend: Increasing"
Note over Backend: ""
Note over Backend: "User question: 'How much did I spend on food\nthis month?'"
Note over Backend: ""
Note over Backend: "Provide a helpful, conversational response."

LLM -> LLM: Process with LLM model
LLM -> LLM: Generate response

LLM --> Backend: {response:
Note over LLM: "You spent ₹2,100 on food this month,\nwhich is ₹100 more than your ₹2,000 budget.\nThis represents a 5% overspend compared\nto your budget. However, your food\nspending is only 5% higher than last\nmonth (₹1,950), so the trend is relatively\nstable. Consider meal planning to stay\nwithin budget next month!"}

Backend -> DB: INSERT INTO chat_history\n(user_id, user_message, assistant_response,\nintent, timestamp)
DB --> Backend: {chat_id}

Backend --> Frontend: {response: {...}}

Note over User,DB: **DISPLAY RESPONSE**

Frontend -> Frontend: Remove "typing..." indicator
Frontend -> Frontend: Add assistant message to chat

Note over Frontend: Chat Display:
Note over Frontend: [User] "How much did I spend on food\nthis month?"
Note over Frontend: [Assistant] "You spent ₹2,100 on food this month..."
Note over Frontend: [Show related data card]
Note over Frontend: Category: Food
Note over Frontend: Spent: ₹2,100 / ₹2,000 budget
Note over Frontend: Status: 5% over budget

Frontend -> Frontend: Scroll to latest message
Frontend --> User: Display assistant response

Note over User,DB: **CONVERSATION CONTINUITY**

User -> Frontend: Type follow-up: "What can I do to reduce it?"
User -> Frontend: Send message

Frontend -> Backend: POST /chat/message\n{message, chat_history: [...all previous messages...]}

Backend -> IntentEng: recognize_intent(message, context=previous_messages)

Note over IntentEng: Intent with context:
Note over IntentEng: Current: "What can I do to reduce it?"
Note over IntentEng: Previous context: Food overspending
Note over IntentEng: Resolved intent: "REDUCTION_RECOMMENDATION"

Backend -> DataFetcher: Fetch user's food spending details
DataFetcher -> DB: SELECT * FROM transactions\nWHERE category='Food' ORDER BY date DESC LIMIT 20
DB --> DataFetcher: detailed_food_transactions

Backend -> LLM: Generate recommendations\nwith context of previous conversation

LLM --> Backend: {response:
Note over LLM: "Here are ways to reduce food spending:\n\n1. Reduce restaurant visits from 3x to 2x weekly\n   Potential savings: ₹400/month\n\n2. Use grocery stores instead of premium markets\n   Potential savings: ₹150/month\n\n3. Set a weekly grocery budget of ₹350\n   Current avg: ₹420/week\n\n4. Take advantage of cashback/loyalty programs\n   Potential savings: ₹100/month\n\nTotal potential monthly savings: ₹650!"}

Backend -> DB: INSERT INTO chat_history
DB --> Backend: {success}

Backend --> Frontend: {response: {...}}
Frontend -> Frontend: Display recommendation
Frontend --> User: Show detailed recommendations

Note over User,DB: **QUICK ACTION BUTTONS**

Frontend -> Frontend: Add action buttons below response

Note over Frontend: Buttons:
Note over Frontend: [Set Food Budget to ₹1,350]
Note over Frontend: [View Food Breakdown]
Note over Frontend: [Show All Spending Tips]

User -> Frontend: Click "Set Food Budget to ₹1,350"
Frontend -> Backend: PUT /budgets/food\n{new_amount: 1350}

Backend -> DB: UPDATE budgets SET amount=1350
DB --> Backend: {success}

Backend --> Frontend: {status: "budget_updated"}
Frontend -> Frontend: Show confirmation in chat
Frontend -> Frontend: Show updated budget

Note over Frontend: Assistant: "Done! I've updated your food\nbudget to ₹1,350. This will help\nyou stay on track!"

Frontend --> User: Display confirmation

Note over User,DB: **MULTI-TURN CONVERSATION**

User -> Frontend: Continue conversation...
User -> Frontend: "How's my financial health?"

Frontend -> Backend: POST /chat/message\n{message, chat_history}

Backend -> IntentEng: Intent = "FINANCIAL_HEALTH_QUERY"

Backend -> DataFetcher: Fetch financial health score
DataFetcher -> DB: Calculate health score
DB --> DataFetcher: score: 75, grade: "B"

Backend -> LLM: Generate response with score data
LLM --> Backend: {response: detailed analysis}

Backend -> Frontend: {response}
Frontend -> Frontend: Render card showing score + response
Frontend --> User: Display health score

Note over User,DB: **CHAT HISTORY & CONTEXT MANAGEMENT**

Backend -> Backend: Maintain conversation context

Note over Backend: Context Management:
Note over Backend: - Keep last 10 messages in memory
Note over Backend: - Extract key facts from conversation
Note over Backend: - Update user profile context
Note over Backend: - Cache frequent queries

Backend -> DB: SELECT * FROM chat_history\nWHERE user_id ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
DB --> Backend: recent_conversations

Backend -> Backend: Summarize conversation
Backend -> Backend: Extract: User concerned about food budget,\ninterested in recommendations

Note over User,DB: **SAVE CHAT SESSION**

User -> Frontend: Navigate away or close chat
Frontend -> Backend: POST /chat/save-session\n{session_data}

Backend -> DB: INSERT INTO chat_sessions\n(user_id, chat_history, insights_generated,\nsession_end_time)
DB --> Backend: {session_id}

Backend --> Frontend: {status: "saved"}

Note over User,DB: **EXPORT CONVERSATION**

User -> Frontend: Click "Export Chat"
Frontend -> Backend: GET /chat/export?session_id

Backend -> DB: Fetch chat history
DB --> Backend: all_messages

Backend -> Backend: Format as PDF/TXT
Backend -> Backend: Add date, summary, recommendations

Backend --> Frontend: {file_url}
Frontend -> Frontend: Download chat transcript
Frontend --> User: Chat exported as PDF

@enduml
